\f[CR]cursorWordBegin()\f[R], \f[CR]cursorViWordBegin()\f[R], \f[CR]cursorBigWordBegin()\f[R]
Move the cursor to the beginning of the current word, or if already
there, to the end of the previous word.
.TP
\f[CR]async getCurrentWord(x = this.cursorx, y = this.cursory)\f[R]
