.TP
\f[CR]findPrevMatch(regex, x, y, wrap = false, n = 1)\f[R], \f[CR]findNextMatch(regex, x, y, wrap = false, n = 1)\f[R]
Find the previous/next match for a regex.
.RS
\f[CR]regex\f[R] is a RegExp object (e.g.\ from
